  "current_stage": "Feishu First runtime with local one-click preflight/start wrappers. PostgreSQL/pgvector remains the primary database and memory base. Feishu events and card.action.trigger callbacks now share the Encrypt Key signature/decrypt/token path; legacy SHA1 card signatures are rejected. Local doctor can initialize .env, generate local runtime secrets without printing them, and now reports OS-appropriate one-click commands: scripts/lietou-oneclick.sh for Linux servers and scripts/lietou-oneclick.ps1 for Windows users. User BYOK model profiles, AgentSOPRegistry, memory retention, ReviewGate, and query-path indexes are implemented locally; real Feishu/Bitable/model/Docker end-to-end validation remains environment-dependent.",
